media_camera Missing person: Mark Browning. Macarthur Help locate missing man Mark Browning Tarik Elmerhebe, Macarthur Chronicle Camden February 21, 2017 2:03pm
POLICE are appealing for assistance to help find Mark Browning, who went missing from Bringelly on Friday.
The 39-year-old was last seen leaving his home in Carrington Rd and failed to return.
Police and Mr Browning’s family have serious concerns for his welfare.
Mr Browning is of a caucasian appearance, medium build, about 180cm tall, with brown hair and a brown beard and moustache.
He has hazel eyes and a full sleeve tattoo on his left arm. He also has tattoos on his right upper arm, back and both sides of his chest.
Mr Browning was last seen wearing a black singlet, shorts, no shoes and a silver necklace.
Anyone with information on Mr Browning’s whereabouts should call Triple Zero (000) immediately.
